  <body>
    <div class="main">
      <div class="wrapper">
        <h1 class="title">Skript Editor</h1>
        <p class="text-wrapper">skript.ml is a web application tool allowing you to easily edit your skript applications.
        </p>
        <a href="app" class="app">Open The App</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="features">
      <h1>
        What is skript?
      </h1>
      <p>
        Skript is an event-based programming language. It's syntax is similar to python. <br>Here's a simple example of Skript in use:
      </p>
      <pre>
        <code>on join:<br>&emsp;send "Welcome to the server! Have fun :D"</code>
      </pre>
      <h1>
        Is there multi-user functionality?
      </h1>
      <p>
        Yes; However, you may have to press CTRL + F5 to reload the server sockets (for real time link sharing and editing).
      </p>
      <h1>
        Is it open source?
      </h1>
      <p>
        Yes! <a href="https://glitch.com/~skript-editor">here</a> is the code.
      </p>
    </div>
    <script src="scripts/main.js" defer></script>
    <script>if (navigator.serviceWorker) navigator.serviceWorker.register('/sw.js', {scope: '/'})</script>
  </body>
